<dt class='comment-author blog-author' id='c238100105750048548'>
<a name='c238100105750048548'></a>
<div class="avatar-image-container vcard"><span dir="ltr"><a href="http://www.blogger.com/profile/04899250633318059069" rel="nofollow" onclick="" class="avatar-hovercard" id="av-73-04899250633318059069"><img src="http://img1.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif" width="35" height="35" alt="" class="delayLoad" style="display: none;" longdesc="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-M3V-EnH6F5g/ToR9-6jBOnI/AAAAAAAACTw/U1ASBN4UeS4/s45/IMG_7857.jpg" title="Eivind Berge">

<noscript><img src="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-M3V-EnH6F5g/ToR9-6jBOnI/AAAAAAAACTw/U1ASBN4UeS4/s45/IMG_7857.jpg" width="35" height="35" class="photo" alt=""></noscript></a></span></div>
