<div class="avatar-image-container vcard"><span dir="ltr"><a href="http://www.blogger.com/profile/01840848846249018854" rel="nofollow" onclick="" class="avatar-hovercard" id="av-81-01840848846249018854"><img src="http://img1.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif" width="35" height="35" alt="" class="delayLoad" style="display: none;" longdesc="http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-2NYmHP9c14o/TjbqB66kz1I/AAAAAAAAAAo/17b1lUNEBlg/s45/IMG_7179.JPG" title="Emma">

