<dt class='comment-author ' id='c1633540262005017820'>
<a name='c1633540262005017820'></a>
<div class="avatar-image-container avatar-stock"><span dir="ltr"><img src="http://img1.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif" width="16" height="16" alt="" title="Jarl Flaaten Bj&oslash;rk">

</span></div>
Jarl Flaaten Bjørk
