<dt class='comment-author ' id='c7695296667329620015'>
<a name='c7695296667329620015'></a>
<div class="avatar-image-container vcard"><span dir="ltr"><a href="http://www.blogger.com/profile/03811958709557074354" rel="nofollow" onclick="" class="avatar-hovercard" id="av-141-03811958709557074354"><img src="http://img1.blogblog.com/img/blank.gif" width="35" height="35" alt="" class="delayLoad" style="display: none;" longdesc="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-GwJJ9rVnVNA/TjRa7TV3QSI/AAAAAAAAAA0/y0l5OeTv8WA/s45/anarki.jpg" title="Ragnarkisten">

<noscript><img src="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-GwJJ9rVnVNA/TjRa7TV3QSI/AAAAAAAAAA0/y0l5OeTv8WA/s45/anarki.jpg" width="35" height="35" class="photo" alt=""></noscript></a></span></div>
<a href='http://www.blogger.com/profile/03811958709557074354' rel='nofollow'>Ragnarkisten</a>
said...
